---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`About - ${siteConfig.title}`}
  description="Olivia Knoedt — software engineer, engineering manager, and tech consultant based in London."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-center sm:items-start mb-12">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div
            class="w-40 h-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-4 border-apricot-cream/50 dark:border-apricot-cream/30"
          >
            <img
              src="https://d19w7e3j8gkywb.cloudfront.net/olivia-2022.webp"
              alt="Olivia Knoedt"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-150 object-middle"
              width="160"
              height="160"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-twilight-indigo dark:text-eggshell">
            Hello, I'm <span class="text-burnt-peach dark:text-muted-teal">Olivia</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-twilight-indigo/80 dark:text-eggshell/90 leading-relaxed">
            Software engineering manager and full-stack engineer specialising in Cloud and DevOps.
            Based in London. I care about diversity in tech, building high-performing teams, and
            tech for good.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section aria-label="My work">
        <nav aria-label="Portfolio sections">
          <ul class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <li class="flex-1">
              <a
                href="/experience"
                class="group flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 bg-eggshell dark:bg-twilight-indigo/50 border border-apricot-cream/40 dark:border-muted-teal/20 rounded-xl hover:border-burnt-peach/60 dark:hover:border-muted-teal/60 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-burnt-peach dark:focus:ring-muted-teal focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-twilight-indigo"
              >
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-twilight-indigo dark:text-eggshell block"
                    >Experience</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-sm text-twilight-indigo/50 dark:text-eggshell/50"
                    >Career history</span
                  >
                </div>
                <span
                  class="text-twilight-indigo/40 dark:text-eggshell/40 group-hover:text-burnt-peach dark:group-hover:text-muted-teal transition-colors"
                  aria-hidden="true">→</span
                >
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="flex-1">
              <a
                href="/projects"
                class="group flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 bg-eggshell dark:bg-twilight-indigo/50 border border-apricot-cream/40 dark:border-muted-teal/20 rounded-xl hover:border-burnt-peach/60 dark:hover:border-muted-teal/60 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-burnt-peach dark:focus:ring-muted-teal focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-twilight-indigo"
              >
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-twilight-indigo dark:text-eggshell block"
                    >Projects</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-sm text-twilight-indigo/50 dark:text-eggshell/50"
                    >Things I've built</span
                  >
                </div>
                <span
                  class="text-twilight-indigo/40 dark:text-eggshell/40 group-hover:text-burnt-peach dark:group-hover:text-muted-teal transition-colors"
                  aria-hidden="true">→</span
                >
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12" aria-label="Social links">
        <nav aria-label="Social media profiles">
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <li>
              <a
                href={siteConfig.social.linkedin}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-apricot-cream text-twilight-indigo rounded-lg hover:bg-apricot-cream/90 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-apricot-cream focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-twilight-indigo font-medium text-sm"
              >
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                LinkedIn
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href={siteConfig.social.github}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-apricot-cream text-twilight-indigo rounded-lg hover:bg-apricot-cream/90 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-apricot-cream focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-twilight-indigo font-medium text-sm"
              >
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                GitHub
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href={siteConfig.social.substackTech}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-apricot-cream text-twilight-indigo rounded-lg hover:bg-apricot-cream/90 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-apricot-cream focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-twilight-indigo font-medium text-sm"
              >
                <i class="fi fi-rr-bookmark w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                Substack
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </section>

      <div
        class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none leading-relaxed space-y-6 mt-12 mb-12"
      >
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I'm a software engineer and engineering manager from London, UK. I've been working in the
          tech industry since 2011 and I graduated from the University of Nottingham with a BSc in
          Computer Science. Since then, I've gained diverse experience through both full-time and
          freelance work across industries such as social impact, automotive, geospatial,
          e-commerce, finance and employee benefits. I've worked across the stack with a variety of
          technologies, services and languages, with a focus on web development. In recent years, my
          work has expanded into leadership, cloud computing, and DevOps.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          From 2017, I spent 3 years at BCGDV in Berlin building start-ups from scratch, leading on
          to a role as Head of Engineering at OpenSC (a joint venture founded by BCGDV & WWF).
          Currently, I'm working with 101 Ways as a Lead Technology Consultant — helping technology
          leaders solve challenging problems and build great digital products. I most recently
          worked on modernising Recharge.com's 16 year-old legacy tech stack, re-platforming from
          scratch and helping the team hire, implement modern software practices, and deliver with
          both speed and quality.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Outside of work, I'm also a parent, balancing career and family life. Over the years, I've
          learned about more than just technology and writing code. I've loved learning about
          personal and team productivity, building strong team dynamics, fostering cross-functional
          collaboration, and understanding what diversity and inclusion means for a company and its
          people. I'm truly passionate about supporting other women and minorities in tech, and I
          love to write and speak.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Let's connect! If you're interested in working together, speaking at an event, or
          collaborating, I'd love to hear from you. Feel free to reach out via{' '}
          <a href={siteConfig.social.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <iframe
        src="https://balancingthestack.substack.com/embed"
        class="substack-embed"
        width="480"
        height="320"
        title="Subscribe to Balancing the Stack on Substack"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
